---
pageImageUrl: "https://mattclaffey.co.uk/thumbnail.jpg"
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: ‚úçüèª I like to share what I learn to help others
desc: I blog on Medium about all the things I learn and I feel that it is so important to share the knowledge with the world about the things I am passionate about.
---

<section class="o-region c-banner" style="--region-bg:var(--banner-bg);--region-text-color:var(--banner-text)">
  <div class="o-region__inner">
    <h1 class="e-heading e-heading--h1 c-banner__title">‚úçüèª I like to share what I learn to help others</h1>
    <p class="e-text c-banner__text u-text--larger@md">
            I blog on Medium about all the things I learn and I feel that it is so important to share the knowledge with the world about the things I am passionate about.
        </p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="o-region">
  <div class="o-region__inner">
    <ol class="c-post-list o-grid">
      {% for post in blog.posts %}
        <li class="c-post-list__item o-grid__item--12/12 o-grid__item--4/12@md">
          <a href="/blog/{{ post.title | slug }}" class="c-post-list__link">
            <span class="u-visually-hidden">Read more about {% if post.title %}{{ post.title }}
              {% else %}
                <code>{{ post.link }}</code>
              {% endif %}</span></a>
          <div class="c-post-list__item-container">
            <picture class="e-picture u-margin--bottom">
              <img src="{{ post.thumbnail }}" loading="lazy" alt="Thumbnail image for {{ post-title }} blog post"/>
            </picture>
            <h3 class="e-heading e-heading--h5">{{ post.title }}</h3>
            <p class="c-post-list__date">
              <time datetime="{{ post.pubDate | htmlDateString }}" class="u-text--smaller">{{ post.pubDate | readableDate }}</time>
            </p>
            <div class="c-post-list__short-description">{{ post.shortDescription | safe }}</div>
            <span class="e-link" aria-hidden="true">Read more</span>
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
